<a name="tab_1-1_340"></a><h2 class="tabber_title">Offers</h2>
<h3><strong>"Weekly STD and SMS Pack"<br /></strong></h3>
<p>Now enjoy weekly STD and SMS pack. Limited period offerings. <strong><a href="/dolphin/index.php/3g-prepaid-plans/gsm-prepaid">Know more....</a></strong></p>
<p>
<hr />
</p>
<p><img style="float: left; margin: 0px;" src="/dolphin/images/stories/sakhi-plan.jpg" alt="" width="325" /></p>
<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>MTNL's new Friends and Family Plan</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>now call at reduced rates of 10 Paisa / minute on&nbsp;selected MTNL numbers.&nbsp;</strong><strong><a href="/dolphin/index.php/component/content/156">Know more...</a></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<hr />
<h3><strong>"Trump Vidyarthi" &amp; "Chota Vidyarthi Plans"<br /></strong></h3>
<p>Now get more with revised Vidyarthi and chota Vidyarthi plans. Limited period offerings. <strong><a href="/dolphin/index.php/component/content/59">Know more....</a></strong></p>
<hr />
<h3><strong>"Free SIM &amp; FRC ALL in One Paisa"<br /></strong></h3>
<p>Enjoy attractive calling rate of 1 paisa / second for all your Local &amp; STD calls to any network, even while roaming, by using MTNL's ALL in One Paisa FRC. <strong><a href="/dolphin/index.php/3g-prepaid-plans?tab=FirstRechargeCoupons">Know more....</a></strong></p>
<hr />
<h3><strong>"Stay connected with High Speed Wireless Broadband"<br /></strong></h3>
<p><img style="float: right;" src="/dolphin/images/stories/teracom-3g-data-card-mtnl.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p>The ultimate super fast experience is here. With MTNL's 3G Wireless Broadband data card gain access to the world of Internet @3.6 Mbps with our state of art 3G network. Now do it all on the move. <strong><a href="/dolphin/index.php/tariff-plans">Know more...</a></strong></p>
